# Fadi Ecosystem

**Read first:** repository root `AGENTS.md` and `philosophy/PRINCIPLES.md`

This workspace uses **Fadi-Core-Platform** as the single source of truth. Application folders contain implementation only.

## Before any work

1. `Fadi-Core-Platform/AGENTS.md`
2. `Fadi-Core-Platform/philosophy/PRINCIPLES.md`
3. `Fadi-Core-Platform/products/{app}.md`
4. App `AGENTS.md` for code paths only

## Current priority

**Figma redesign before code.** No major UI implementation without approved Figma. No repo separation.

## Non-negotiable

Invisible intelligence · one question per screen · behavior over forms · brain-first · no chat-as-product · SmartShop owns household graph

## Platform wins

When app docs conflict with platform docs, platform wins. ADRs in `Fadi-Core-Platform/decisions/`.

## Anti-patterns

Macro dashboards as home · long onboarding · Coach tab · Analytics tab · "AI" on free tier · duplicate household profiles · pantry UI in v1

Full list: `Fadi-Core-Platform/philosophy/PRINCIPLES.md`
